    <div class="header">ABOUT</div>
    <div class="msg-box">So Who Is Michael Rubino?</div>
    <p>That is the million dollar question, isn't it? I'm a <span id="aboutAge"></span> year old fellow from the town of Freeport, New York out on Long Island. Over the years I've jumped around to other places like Boston, Scottsdale, and Decatur, finally setting up shop in good old Atlanta.</p>
    <p>I definitely consider myself a bit of a ham. I always enjoy getting people to laugh and enjoy themselves when I can. People say I'm a caring and amiable person too. Ultimately I just want to help make the world a little better if I can, and web development is yet another avenue for me to do just that.</p>
